data.description: This 2 Story 2 Bedroom Home in the Heart of Scottdale has Been Lovingly Taken Care of For 17 Yrs! Great Floor Plan for Entertaining. The Fully Equipped Kitchen is Laid Out to Make Cooking a Breeze and has Plenty of Cabinets and Counter Space. The Neutral Backsplash will go with any Decor! Step out onto the Maintenance Free Deck to Grill or Enjoy Your Morning Coffee. The Dining Room Can Accommodate a Large Table for all of Your Family and Friends! Unwind in the 17x11 Living Room or on the Covered Front Porch. Get Cozy in the Huge Bedroom with an Electric Fireplace and 2 Separate Closets! Mature Landscaping and Well Kept, Usable Yard with a Shed for Your Lawn and Gardening Tools. Furnace and A/C Only 2 Years Old, New Windows During Ownership. The Clean and Dry Basement has Tons of Storage, Workout and Office Area, and a Laundry Room with Access to a Patio underneath the Deck and to the Spacious Backyard. All Appliances Including Washer/Dryer Stay! This Home has it all!
